<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<index version="1" name="FinestCardboardPearls Scripts">
  <metadata>
    <description><![CDATA[Scripts for Rock Band 3 song authoring in REAPER.

**FCP Song Progress Tracker** - Multi-tab interface for tracking song authoring progress with FX chain alignment, screenset & visible note row management, creating practice sections and turning them into Regions, and integrations with other charting tools.

**FCP Spectracular Patcher** - Patches talagan's Spectracular with helpful vocals charting functionality: viewport persistence, modified mouse wheel behavior (vertical pan, Ctrl+wheel vertical zoom, Alt+wheel horizontal zoom), MIDI note overlay with lyrics, note preview on click, and smaller minimum window size.

**FCP Venue Preview Lighting Camera** - Animated sprite previewer for Rock Band 3 venue camera cuts, lighting cues, and post-processing effects.

**FCP Lyrics Clipboard** - Paste lyrics and automatically assign them to sequential MIDI notes. Saves lyrics per-region.

Additional utility scripts for MIDI editing, tempo prediction, and difficulty switching are also included.
]]></description>
  </metadata>
