    <reapack name="FCP Predict Tempo Markers.lua" type="script">
      <version name="0.6" author="FinestCardboardPearls">
        <changelog><![CDATA[Predict Tempo Markers

Features:
- Analyzes drum transients and predicts optimal tempo marker placements
- Fits tempo changes so musical grid subdivisions (16ths/triplets) align with transients
- Multiple prediction options with different sensitivities
- Time signature detection and configuration
- Navigation buttons for transient jumping and time selection
]]></changelog>
